{"tid":1468596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷靜思考，其實今日好大程度係一個局，目的就係分化","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:50:58.000Z","uid":98855,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"50ec6d501deaf9a5782580600310ad5bbcf96805","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:21:36.000Z","msg":"我都知連登、TG、Facebook，而家分化風應該吹得好勁，但仲有一絲希望，點樣都要講我想講嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n發夢今日係現場，完咗睇返成件事，簡直覺得係一個局：<br />\n<br />\n一. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今日捉到異常多鬼</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得今日嗰啲俾人捉到嘅鬼，簡直好似就係特登俾你捉咁。<br />\n<br />\n首先，邊個會無啦啦隨身袋住件<span style=\"color: blue;\">我愛警察</span>tee入機場，然後再行跡可疑咁俾你發現，黃咗之後唔係落荒而逃，而係全世界面前展現件tee。<br />\n<br />\n淨係呢點已經好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n要知道如果真係做鬼嘅，大多數你都好發現。當然可以話經過811之後大家警惕咗好多，但同時，啲狗都會更加警惕。今日咁高調咁搵到咁多隻，簡直好似特登俾你搵。<br />\n<br />\n二. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好多帶頭圍嘅「勇武」都好可疑</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有一啲「勇武」發現鬼之後異常激動，帶頭叫人群圍佢，令到大家都好古厝、好激動，但好快自己閃走咗。<br />\n<br />\n三. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>分化風吹到周圍都係</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n先係吹尋日<span style=\"font-size: large;\">清場論</span>，令到好多所謂和理非走咗，牽起留低嘅勇武同和理非內哄互屌。一方屌對面散水，另一方屌對面戀戰、唔hit and run。<br />\n<br />\n之後到今日再俾大家睇「勇武」捉鬼，令到兩方撕裂更加大。 <br />\n<br />\n重點係，林鄭今日個記招，對於機場俾人圍，totally don&rsquo;t give a shit，即係話其實佢根本就唔會覺得呢件事成氣候。好大機會係知道香港人最大嘅弱點在於內哄，其實佢根本上唔使做啲咩，呢個危機就自己會拆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原本我哋以為機場隻牌好有bargaining，反而變成和理非同勇武決裂嘅點，成功扭轉成個局面。<br />\n<br />\n今日隔離台開post，叫大家唔好低估popo，其實林奠都係。<br />\n對住佢哋，我哋唯有更加謹慎、小心同冷靜去思考同處理每一個情況。<br />\n<br />\n革命維持咗兩個月，唔輸嘅唯一方法就係冷靜睇清楚對家打緊咩牌。<br />\n<br />\n五年前，天琦主張勇武，好多人都唔信呢個係出路，到五年後先發現原來佢俾我哋行得前。然後呢個時候香港已經變得好差。<br />\n<br />\n五年後，天琦係獄中叫我哋「不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，更要始終保持自己理性的思考。」<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋已經知道天琦俾我哋行得前，今次就更加應該要信佢。<br />\n<br />\n既然根本唔能夠排除邊啲係鬼，大家與其屌勇武，不如相信在場嘅真勇武係可以點到即止，唔會盲目暴力。<br />\n<br />\n冷靜思考，相信同路人，先係我哋可以贏對家嘅方法。 <br />\n<br />\n我哋已經唔撚可以輸㗎啦"},{"pid":"c254e96d0b85decafbc9c41267be762e4139bc87","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:20.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0a43775090d91b6a3425b6bf119a6ef1b2a874","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:34.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7c7b81f03502e9c1fa5ceb3c08e2803cd1a07a","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:48.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5de6e977717f87cf694b743dbc3d5548b1c39b8","tid":1468596,"uid":257184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:59.000Z","msg":"我都覺得今日成件事勁奇怪<br />\n我哋真係冇必要攬埋啲鬼，不割蓆不分化不篤灰唔係俾大家濫用，無理由無目的純發洩嘅事，大家唔好再做，有人做都要阻止，運動先可以繼續"},{"pid":"7a75d045733929fea70493086c32c254f645ac72","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:11.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00754445f0021745dbc54f5754b2e7041096d05","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5de6e977717f87cf694b743dbc3d5548b1c39b8","tid":1468596,"uid":257184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:59.000Z","msg":"我都覺得今日成件事勁奇怪<br />\n我哋真係冇必要攬埋啲鬼，不割蓆不分化不篤灰唔係俾大家濫用，無理由無目的純發洩嘅事，大家唔好再做，有人做都要阻止，運動先可以繼續"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:26:07.000Z","msg":"係！！！然後係啦啦10幾架狗車高調進場，諗返都覺得其實根本冇意思！！！"},{"pid":"98fddd736f9f2ba363a1f39e1876be392ad34a1b","tid":1468596,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:27:09.000Z","msg":"捉到共狗又唔想就咁放走，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n貼住「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類，<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰並唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其象徵意義。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"f738de889d0ac60c475b379e2a32d4c2e734c3f2","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:27:17.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf70d63c34b951c7a437e15c8c7e0ef87a485b3b","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:27:49.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d9b811980c95054057b8a749c0bb517628ea3e","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:29:16.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97621c777d595bb7ca7f75f01b0e54f5e070115","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:31:21.000Z","msg":"二. 好多帶頭圍嘅「勇武」都好可疑<br />\n<br />\n有一啲「勇武」發現鬼之後異常激動，帶頭叫人群圍佢，令到大家都好古厝、好激動，但好快自己閃走咗。<br />\n<br />\n三. 分化風吹到周圍都係<br />\n<br />\n先係吹尋日清場論，令到好多所謂和理非走咗，牽起留低嘅勇武同和理非內哄互屌。一方屌對面散水，另一方屌對面戀戰、唔hit and run。<br />\n<br />\n之後到今日再俾大家睇「勇武」捉鬼，令到兩方撕裂更加大。 <br />\n<br />\n重點係，林鄭今日個記招，對於機場俾人圍，totally don&rsquo;t give a shit，即係話其實佢根本就唔會覺得呢件事成氣候。好大機會係知道香港人最大嘅弱點在於內哄，其實佢根本上唔使做啲咩，呢個危機就自己會拆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原本我哋以為機場隻牌好有bargaining，反而變成和理非同勇武決裂嘅點，成功扭轉成個局面。"},{"pid":"6fed0752206531624bc3499721e58501f6ed189b","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:32:56.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1cd876c011f108c9e35cf14f29c4dfdb060f23","tid":1468596,"uid":304860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:34:02.000Z","msg":"唔好發泄，機場和理非<br />\n<br />\n唔阻人 check in<br />\n<br />\n唔好亂抓鬼<br />\n<br />\n唔好打記者，救護，人道主義者<br />\n<br />\n即使發現鬼，影低證物同人樣，然後趕拒走，但唔好打人<br />\n留低既證據比文宣好好發揮，系好好既材料<br />\n<br />\n唔好阻救護做野，即使系對象官媒，公安，敵人，同鬼<br />\n<br />\n戴實個口罩，就唔驚影大頭相<br />\n<br />\n盡量保持禮貌，冷靜應對<br />\n<br />\n唔好阻記者拍攝<br />\n<br />\n以上系小弟既幾點建議"},{"pid":"715f38ed8572862b71d7be7f001db8c09ac051f8","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:37:11.000Z","msg":"唔撚割蓆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日係林奠個局！！"},{"pid":"6eca343511d51f65b1036554d849f4ec148939c3","tid":1468596,"uid":236518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:39:05.000Z","msg":"［機場抗爭］呢條計好惡毒，大家幫手推上熱門睇下點拆<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEixAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEixAS</a>"},{"pid":"db2716641bf5858edd6c6205aaccdc8d0f9fdb66","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:39:26.000Z","msg":"唔撚可以輸！推到分化撚睇到！"},{"pid":"3e18afb98b68a1c02d57320fe1d56fad9c1d0e21","tid":1468596,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:40:07.000Z","msg":"必須小心！"},{"pid":"969407f7a40d62aaf218bce9099251472b49de27","tid":1468596,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:40:54.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"267d5f3203fca37a2139e1c436c888920f28bcaa","tid":1468596,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:41:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89b4b1a949ef05ebfe1446b1787bc1ce9e7a6be8","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e18afb98b68a1c02d57320fe1d56fad9c1d0e21","tid":1468596,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:40:07.000Z","msg":"必須小心！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:43:40.000Z","msg":"救港方法！冷靜 獨立 思考！"},{"pid":"b6e602ad3ac0977a8756d56469c5ef1880b703ca","tid":1468596,"uid":265257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:45:36.000Z","msg":"推到分化撚睇到！"},{"pid":"9a87fbf967f8b934436b20e2f256b6d435ee4c1b","tid":1468596,"uid":98855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6e602ad3ac0977a8756d56469c